Package: segregr
Type: Package
Title: Spatial Segregation Metrics for Areal Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Marcus", "Saraiva", email = "marcus.saraiva@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6218-2338"))
Description: Calculates spatial and aspatial segregation metrics for areal
    data. Implements generalised spatial versions of the Dissimilarity index,
    Theil's Entropy and Information Theory indices (measures of evenness), and
    the Isolation and Exposure indices. Both global and local variants of each
    metric are provided, with optional Gaussian spatial smoothing controlled
    by a bandwidth parameter.
